---
import BaseLayout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const lang = "en";
---

<BaseLayout
  lang={lang}
  title="Parent Space — Le Ballon Rouge"
  description="Guide, fees, menu and useful resources to support your child at Le Ballon Rouge."
>

  <!-- Page intro -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 pb-10 pt-8 md:pt-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-black tracking-tight md:text-5xl">Parent Space</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 max-w-prose text-base font-medium leading-7 text-slate-600 md:text-lg">
      Guide, fees, menu and useful resources to support your child at Le Ballon Rouge.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a
        href="/en/inscription/"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-red-700 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold text-white shadow-lg shadow-red-700/20 hover:bg-red-800"
      >
        How to register
      </a>
      <a
        href="#guide"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white/80 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-800 shadow-sm hover:bg-white"
      >
        Parent guide
      </a>
      <a
        href="#frais"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white/80 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-800 shadow-sm hover:bg-white"
      >
        Fees & subsidies
      </a>
      <a
        href="#menu"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white/80 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-800 shadow-sm hover:bg-white"
      >
        Menu
      </a>
      <a
        href="#ressources"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white/80 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-800 shadow-sm hover:bg-white"
      >
        Resources
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Parent guide -->
  <section id="guide" class="scroll-mt-28 mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 pb-12">
    <div class="rounded-[28px] border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-black/5 md:p-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-black tracking-tight md:text-2xl">Parent guide</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
        The daycare centre provides families with a guide containing useful information (registration and withdrawal, arrivals and departures, authorized persons,
        personal belongings, statutory holidays, vacations, illness, medication administration, supervision, etc.).
      </p>

      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a
          href="/docs/guide-des-parents.pdf"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold shadow-sm hover:bg-white/80"
        >
          Download the guide (PDF)
        </a>
        <a
          href="/en/contact/"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white/80 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-800 shadow-sm hover:bg-white"
        >
          Have a question? Contact us
        </a>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500">
        Tip: if the PDF is not ready yet, leave the button as a placeholder and add the file later.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Fees & subsidies -->
  <section id="frais" class="scroll-mt-28 mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 pb-12">
    <div class="rounded-[28px] border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-black/5 md:p-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-black tracking-tight md:text-2xl">Fees and subsidies</h2>

      <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
        Le Ballon Rouge is enrolled in the Canada-wide early learning and child care system; please note that this does not apply to miscellaneous fees
        (field trips, late pickup fees, non-sufficient funds, etc.).
      </p>

      <div class="mt-6 rounded-2xl border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-5">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-black">Base fees (2025)</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 leading-7 text-slate-600">
          Paste the "Base Fees 2025" table here (Hamilton + Brantford) from the Word document.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500">
          (When you paste the raw table, I'll reformat it into a clean Markdown table.)
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-6 grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2">
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-5">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-black">Late pickup fees</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 leading-7 text-slate-600">
            A late pickup penalty applies. A fee of $10.00 per 15 minutes, per family, is payable directly to staff (cash only)
            when children are picked up late, according to the daycare's clock.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 font-bold text-slate-700">
            <li>0 to 15 minutes: $10.00 / family.</li>
            <li>16 to 30 minutes: $20.00 / family.</li>
            <li>31 to 45 minutes: $30.00 / family.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500">
            No tax receipt is issued for late fees (penalty, not a regular childcare fee).
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-5">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-black">Returned payment</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 leading-7 text-slate-600">
            In the event of a returned or failed payment (cheque, EFT or PAD), a $20.00 fee is added to cover banking and administrative costs.
          </p>

          <h3 class="mt-5 text-lg font-black">Important notes</h3>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 font-bold text-slate-700">
            <li>Rates vary by program and frequency.</li>
            <li>No adjustment for absences, illness or vacations.</li>
            <li>Part-time: fixed days, non-exchangeable (ratio requirements apply).</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-6 rounded-2xl border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-5">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-black">Subsidies (Ontario)</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 leading-7 text-slate-600">
          Ontario residents may be eligible for a full or partial subsidy depending on their financial situation; eligibility is managed by the city.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 font-bold text-slate-700">
          <li>Brantford (Child Care Services): 519-759-7009, 220 Colborne Street, Brantford.</li>
          <li>Hamilton (Early Years & Child Care Services): 905-546-4870.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Menu -->
  <section id="menu" class="scroll-mt-28 mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 pb-12">
    <div class="rounded-[28px] border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-black/5 md:p-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-black tracking-tight md:text-2xl">Menu</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
        Add the menu (PDF) or the monthly menu here when available.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a
          href="/docs/menu.pdf"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold shadow-sm hover:bg-white/80"
        >
          Download the menu (PDF)
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Resources -->
  <section id="ressources" class="scroll-mt-28 mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 pb-12">
    <div class="rounded-[28px] border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-black/5 md:p-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-black tracking-tight md:text-2xl">Resources for parents</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
        We collaborate with partners and community resources to support children, families and staff as needed.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-5">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-black">Community resources</h3>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 font-bold text-slate-700">
            <li>EarlyON Programs.</li>
            <li>Public Health (Hamilton / Brantford).</li>
            <li>Child development support (e.g. Lansdowne Children's Centre, Community Living).</li>
          </ul>
        </article>

        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-5">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-black">Family communication</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 leading-7 text-slate-600">
            Staff connect with families at drop-off and pick-up, and also share information (programming, special days,
            events and resources) through communication tools and group postings.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
            Parent involvement is always welcome, including during special activities or through the board of directors.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-6 rounded-2xl border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-5">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-black">Accessibility & inclusion</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 leading-7 text-slate-600">
          Children with special needs can be integrated into the program with a positive approach; we encourage early screening,
          prevention and collaboration with available resources.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>